  "prompt": "What kind of questions can I ask to Quora?",
  "response": "You can ask a wide variety of questions on Quora, spanning numerous topics and interests. Here are some categories of questions you might consider:\n\n1. **General Knowledge:**\n   - What are the major causes of climate change?\n   - How does the stock market work?\n\n2. **Personal Advice:**\n   - How can I improve my time management skills?\n   - What are some effective ways to deal with stress?\n\n3. **Professional Guidance:**\n   - What skills are essential for a career in data science?\n   - How can I prepare for a job interview at a tech company?\n\n4. **Education:**\n   - What are the best resources for learning Python programming?\n   - How can I improve my writing skills?\n\n5. **Health and Fitness:**\n   - What are the benefits of intermittent fasting?\n   - How can I create a balanced workout routine?\n\n6. **Travel:**\n   - What are some must-see attractions in Paris?\n   - How can I travel on a budget?\n\n7. **Technology:**\n   - What are the latest trends in artificial intelligence?\n   - How does blockchain technology work?\n\n8. **Relationships:**\n   - How can I build trust in a relationship?\n   - What are some red flags in a friendship?\n\n9. **Entertainment:**\n   - What are some underrated movies to watch?\n   - Who are the top musicians in 2023?\n\n10. **Philosophy and Ethics:**\n    - What is the meaning of life?\n    - Is it ever morally acceptable to lie?\n\n11. **DIY and Home Improvement:**\n    - How can I remodel my kitchen on a budget?\n    - What are some tips for growing a garden?\n\n12. **Language and Communication:**\n    - How can I become fluent in Spanish?\n    - What are some tips for effective public speaking?\n\nFeel free to ask questions that are specific to your interests or needs. Quora has a diverse community of users who can provide insights and answers based on their expertise and experiences.",
